   "source": [
    "# 1次元場PDE - 応用編 -"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Burgers方程式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from scipy.integrate import solve_ivp "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "ナビエストークス方程式の移流項$u\\partial_x u$と粘性項$\\partial_{xx} u$のみを考慮する．\n",
    "$$\n",
    "    \\partial_t u + \\lambda_1 u\\partial_x u = \\lambda_2 \\partial_{xx} u\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "移流拡散方程式とも呼ばれている．"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# parameters\n",
    "nx = 100\n",
    "Δx = 1.0/(nx-1)\n",
    "λ1 = 1.0; λ2 = 0.1; \n",
    "# init\n",
    "x  = np.linspace(0.0,1.0,nx) \n",
    "u  = np.zeros_like(x)\n",
    "u[10:30]  = 1.0\n",
    "init   = u\n",
    "# time\n",
    "t_span = [0.,0.5]\n",
    "t_eval = np.linspace(*t_span,50) # time for sampling\n",
    "# ODEs\n",
    "def ODEs(t,u,λ1,λ2,Δx):\n",
    "    du = - λ1 * (np.diff(u)/(Δx))[1:] + λ2 * np.diff(u,2)/(Δx**2)\n",
    "    return np.hstack([0.0,du,0.0])\n",
    "# solve\n",
    "sol = solve_ivp(ODEs,t_span,init,method=\"RK45\",t_eval=t_eval,args=(λ1,λ2,Δx))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "進行しながら滑らかになる様子が見れる．"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x7fa970952ac0>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 3,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },

   ],
   "source": [
    "fig,ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "ax.imshow(sol.y.T,cmap='jet')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## KdV方程式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "コルトヴェーグと，ド・フリースにより定式化された．非線形波を表す方程式．\n",
    "$$\n",
    "    \\partial_t u + 6u \\partial_x u + \\partial_{xxx}u=0\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "パラメータは，この論文を参考にさせていただいた．\n",
    "http://advances.sciencemag.org/content/3/4/e1602614"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# parameters\n",
    "nx = 200\n",
    "Δx = 60./(nx-1)\n",
    "# init\n",
    "x  = np.linspace(0.0,60.0,nx) \n",
    "u  = np.exp(-((x-10.0)/(5.0))**2)\n",
    "init   = u\n",
    "# time\n",
    "t_span = [0.,20.0]\n",
    "t_eval = np.linspace(*t_span,100) # time for sampling\n",
    "# ODEs\n",
    "def ODEs(t,u,Δx):\n",
    "    du = - 6 * u[2:-2] * np.convolve(u,[1.,0.,-1.],'valid')[1:-1]/(2*Δx) - np.diff(u,3)[1:]/(Δx**3)\n",
    "    return np.hstack([0.,0.,du,0.,0.])\n",
    "# solve\n",
    "sol = solve_ivp(ODEs,t_span,init,method=\"RK45\",t_eval=t_eval,args=(Δx,),rtol=1e-8)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "正規分布の初期速度を置いた．時間の進行とともに幾つかの孤立波になる．"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [

    "ax.imshow(sol.y.T,cmap='jet')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## KS方程式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "蔵元ーシバシンスキー方程式．火砕流の挙動を表すよう定式化された．4階微分が特徴的．拡散の強さが拡散する．\n",
    "$$\n",
    "    \\partial_t u + u\\partial_x u + \\partial_{xx} u + \\partial_{xxxx} u = 0\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# parameters\n",
    "nx = 200\n",
    "Δx = 100./(nx-1)\n",
    "# init\n",
    "x  = np.linspace(0.0,60.0,nx) \n",
    "u  = np.exp(-((x-40.0)/(5.0))**2) + np.exp(-((x-60.0)/(5.0))**2)\n",
    "init   = u\n",
    "# time\n",
    "t_span = [0.,100.0]\n",
    "t_eval = np.linspace(*t_span,100) # time for sampling\n",
    "# ODEs\n",
    "def ODEs(t,u,Δx):\n",
    "    du = - u[2:-2] * np.convolve(u,[1.,0.,-1.],'valid')[1:-1]/(2*Δx)\\\n",
    "         - np.diff(u,2)[1:-1]/(Δx**2)\\\n",
    "         - np.diff(u,4)      /(Δx**4)\n",
    "    return np.hstack([0.,0.,du,0.,0.])\n",
    "# solve\n",
    "sol = solve_ivp(ODEs,t_span,init,method=\"RK45\",t_eval=t_eval,args=(Δx,),rtol=1e-8)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "インパクトあって目に楽しい図ができる"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [

   ]

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Schorodinger方程式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "理系大学生の関門として名高いシュレディンガー方程式．数値計算を通してイメージを掴んでみよう．\n",
    "一次元では，定数を1，二次関数型のポテンシャル場$V(x)=x^2/2$を考えると以下の形で書ける．\n",
    "$$\n",
    "    i\\partial_t \\Psi = -\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\partial_{xx}- \\frac{x^2}{2}\\right)\\Psi\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "ちなみにsolve_ivpはcomplexもrealと変わらず扱える．すごい!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# parameters\n",
    "nx = 200\n",
    "Δx = 15./(nx-1)\n",
    "# init\n",
    "x  = np.linspace(-7.5,7.5,nx) \n",
    "Ψ  = 2.*np.exp(-x**2) + 0.j\n",
    "init   = Ψ\n",
    "# time\n",
    "t_span = [0.,20.0]\n",
    "t_eval = np.linspace(*t_span,400) # time for sampling\n",
    "# ODEs\n",
    "def ODEs(t,Ψ,Δx):\n",
    "    dΨ = -1.j*(- 0.5*np.diff(Ψ,2)/(Δx**2) + 0.5*(x**2*Ψ)[1:-1])\n",
    "    return np.hstack([0.+0.j,dΨ,0.+0.j])\n",
    "# solve\n",
    "sol = solve_ivp(ODEs,t_span,init,method=\"RK45\",t_eval=t_eval,args=(Δx,),rtol=1e-8)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "ポテンシャルによって電子波が中心にトラップされている．"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},

  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Non-linear Schirodinger方程式"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "ポテンシャル関数が$V(x)=|\\Psi|^2$(引力)のときも有名．\n",
    "$$\n",
    "    i\\partial_t \\Psi = -\\left(\\frac{1}{2}\\partial_{xx}+ |\\Psi|^2\\right)\\Psi\n",
    "$$\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# parameters\n",
    "nx = 200\n",
    "Δx = 10./(nx-1)\n",
    "# init\n",
    "x  = np.linspace(-5.0,5.0,nx) \n",
    "Ψ  = 2.*np.exp(-x**2) + 0.j\n",
    "init   = Ψ\n",
    "# time\n",
    "t_span = [0.,np.pi]\n",
    "t_eval = np.linspace(*t_span,400) # time for sampling\n",
    "# ODEs\n",
    "def ODEs(t,Ψ,Δx):\n",
    "    dΨ = -1.j*(- 0.5*np.diff(Ψ,2)/(Δx**2) - (np.abs(Ψ)**2*Ψ)[1:-1])\n",
    "    return np.hstack([0.+0.j,dΨ,0.+0.j])\n",
    "# solve\n",
    "sol = solve_ivp(ODEs,t_span,init,method=\"RK45\",t_eval=t_eval,args=(Δx,),rtol=1e-8)"
   ]
  },
